Title: العدد العاشر من مجلة السندباد الصادر عام 1946
Description.note: Published in 1946, this document includes the 10th issue of Sindbad Magazine. It's an Egyptian magazine with a motto on its cover: "A magazine for the new generation." This magazine includes short stories, zajal and translated stories.|~|العدد العاشر من مجلة السندباد الصادر عام 1946، وهي مجلة مصرية على غلافها شعار: "مجلة للنشء الجديد"، تتضمن تعتمد قصص قصيرة وزجل وقصص مترجمة.
References: Mazen Da'na (Son of the collection owner Emair Da'na), interview with PMDA researcher Lama Ghosheh, June 2018, non-transcript, the Palestinian Museum Digital Archive.
Series & Collection: Omair Da'na Sub-collection 3: Miscellaneous Magazines | The Omair Da'na Collection
